Description: # bhammer
        
        This is a Python tool to create an ASCII art banner for a command line tool.
        
        ## Usage
        ### Install
        
        ``` sh
        $ pip install bhammer
        ```
        ### How to use
        Run the program and input the necessary information:
        ```sh
        python -m bhammer
        ```
        
        For more things I did, see my [website](https://www.noxtal.com).
        
